extends layout

block content
  p This view represents the Model-View-Controller (MVC) pattern by separating database query logic (Model) and routing controller logic (Controller) from the user interface representation (View).
  
  h2 Database Table (test_table) Records
  p The data below is queried from the MySQL database container and dynamically rendered into this table template using Pug iteration.

  table
    thead
      <tr>
        <th>ID</th>
        <th>Name</th>
        <th>Email</th>
        <th>Role</th>
      </tr>
    tbody
      each record in data
        tr
          <td><span class="badge">#{record.id}</span></td>
          <td><strong>#{record.name}</strong></td>
          <td>#{record.email}</td>
          <td>#{record.role}</td>

  h2 Database Bullet Point List (Exercise 1)
  p This list renders only the names as bullet points, fulfilling the first database iteration exercise.
  
  .list-container
    each record in data
      .list-item
        .bullet
        span= record.name
